01:43:08.858 --> 01:43:11.942
Rosaleda Street 18B. Santiago.

1280
01:43:12.775 --> 01:43:16.442
Rosaleda Street 18B.
Santiago de Compostela.

1281
01:43:17.025 --> 01:43:18.983
